parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rack and Pinion Steering Gear Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering gear can cause loss of control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks to one side
loss of control
steering gear breaks off from the chassis
rack and pinion disconnects
loss of steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion-Induced Failure of Spare Tire Retainer
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the spare tire retainer can cause the spare tire to detach from its mount and fall to the road while the vehicle is in operation, potentially leading to accidents or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The spare tire falls off the vehicle while driving
the spare tire is loose or detached from its mount.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the frame can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The frame breaks or cracks while driving
the vehicle becomes unstable or difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cross member can cause loss of steering control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The cross member that holds the rack and pinion steering breaks
the steering becomes difficult or impossible to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine compartment fires can cause significant damage to the vehicle, pose a risk to the occupants, and lead to potential accidents or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down without warning
a fire starts in the engine compartment
often accompanied by smoke or flames.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden engine shutdown can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down or stalls without warning
often without any prior indication or warning signs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can prevent the seat belt from functioning properly, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle breaks or fails to latch
the plastic component of the buckle where it attaches to the belt fails
the buckle is difficult to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can prevent the seat belt from functioning properly, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt is difficult to pull out of the retractor
the seat belt does not retract properly
the seat belt is stuck in the retractor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake wear can lead to reduced stopping power, increased risk of accidents, and loss of control, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Squealing or grinding noises when applying the brakes
vibrations when braking
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pads or drums need to be replaced prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake drum failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding or screeching noises when applying the brakes
vibrations when braking
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake drum cracks or fails
loss of braking power.
